# Changelog

All notable changes to T8D will be documented in this file.

## [v1.0.0] - 05 October 2025

### Added

- Complete offline-first task management system
- Progressive Web App (PWA) with installation support
- Task lists and subtasks with nested hierarchy
- Dark/light theme
- Backup and restore functionality (JSON export/import)
- Keyboard shortcuts for quick task creation
- IndexedDB storage for offline data persistence
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop

